# TASK 03 - Build & Smoke

## Goal
Install dependencies and verify the CLI by generating an artifact into the current turn folder.

## Output (authoritative)
- ${artifact_root}/${TURN_ID}/artifacts/codebase.md

## Preconditions
- TASK 02 completed
- Node.js 20 and npm present
- TURN_ID exported in the environment or supplied as variable

## Steps
1. npm install
2. mkdir -p ${artifact_root}/${TURN_ID}/artifacts
3. node bin/cli.js \
   --root . \
   --format md \
   --out ${artifact_root}/${TURN_ID}/artifacts/codebase.md \
   --include "src/**,package.json" \
   --exclude ".git/**,node_modules/**"
4. If the command fails, stop and output logs. Otherwise, record the artifact path in the turn manifest if available.
